OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FThe end of term is an emotional time
OL,7,Ffor many - for children saying goodbye
OL,8,Fto their friends as they prepare to
OL,9,Fmove schools and for parents as they
OL,10,Fwatch their children grow up in the
OL,11,Fblink of an eye.
OL,13,FBut for one West Country mum, the end
OL,14,Fof the school term is emotional for
OL,15,Fanother reason.
OL,17,FSarah, not her real name, looks on
OL,18,Fwith pride as her friends' children
OL,19,Freach new milestones. But she has a
OL,20,Fhidden pain, as she remains uncertain
OL,21,Fand fearful about her own son's future.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
