OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FHer son is autistic and non-verbal. He
OL,7,Fis due to start primary school in
OL,8,FSeptember 2024.
OL,10,FShe says the mainstream primary school
OL,11,Fhe has been offered will not be able
OL,12,Fto meet his needs and he needs to
OL,13,Fattend a specialist school.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
