OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FSarah* is currently in a legal battle
OL,7,Fwith her local authority, which is why
OL,8,FITV News is not identifying her or her
OL,9,Fson. She is set to go to a tribunal,
OL,10,Fbut it will not take place until
OL,11,Fsummer 2025 - meaning she is facing
OL,12,Fhome-schooling her son for the next
OL,13,Fyear at least.
OL,15,FShe said: "I sit back and I look at my
OL,16,Fchildren and it actually scares me
OL,17,Fwhat the future holds. I can't give
OL,18,Fthem what they need and what they
OL,19,Fdeserve and it's out of my hands
OL,20,Fcompletely."
