OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FThe shocking scale of a crisis within
OL,7,Fthe provision for children with
OL,8,Fspecial educational needs has been
OL,9,Frevealed by an ITV investigation.
OL,11,FAcross the West Country, hundreds of
OL,12,Ffamilies are having to go to court
OL,13,Fevery year to fight for the right
OL,14,Fschool place for their children. Often
OL,15,Fchildren are spending months,
OL,16,Fsometimes years, out of education.
OL,18,FFor Sarah*, having to go to a tribunal
OL,19,Fis also adding more stress in an
OL,20,Falready difficult situation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
