OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,F"When you go through a tribunal, you
OL,7,Fget a date given to you with a lot of
OL,8,Fpaperwork. That is extremely
OL,9,Foverwhelming, a lot of wording in
OL,10,Fthere. It's really difficult to
OL,11,Funderstand," she said.
OL,13,FShe said this is often "too much" for
OL,14,Fparents like her, who are already
OL,15,Fstruggling with the day to day
OL,16,Fchallenges of having a child with
OL,17,Fadditional needs.
OL,19,F"The daily battles - getting dressed,
OL,20,Fthe worry of him running off. He has
OL,21,Fno understanding of danger, of risk."
