OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FShe said a slight noise might trigger
OL,7,Fa meltdown for her son and disrupt him
OL,8,Ffor the rest of the day.
OL,10,F"It's like that 'fight mode' is always
OL,11,Fthere and the worry at night when
OL,12,Fwe're going to bed - you know,
OL,13,Fsomething happened today, is it going
OL,14,Fto affect his day tomorrow? Then you
OL,15,Fthrow in the fact that one thing that
OL,16,Fhe's entitled to is his education and
OL,17,Fhe's not getting that."
OL,26,@rD@AOUyD@WO]
