OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,FSarah* has joined support groups to
OL,7,Fget help and advice from other parents
OL,8,Fin similar situations, but says the
OL,9,Fpicture she sees is not a good one.
OL,11,F"It scares me, absolutely scares me,"
OL,12,Fshe said. "Not only do so many
OL,13,Fchildren not have any form of
OL,14,Feducation, but their parents are
OL,15,Fstruggling - the mental health of
OL,16,Fparents is is just crippling,
OL,17,Fabsolutely crippling.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@eO]tD@KOU
