OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,F"I myself have spoken to many parents
OL,7,Fwho are at the end and don't know
OL,8,Fwhere to turn now and that and they're
OL,9,Fready to give up."
OL,11,FIn response to the ITV News
OL,12,Finvestigation, Education Secretary
OL,13,FBridget Phillipson said: "This
OL,14,Fdiagnosis is damning: educational
OL,15,Foutcomes for children with SEND are
OL,16,Fflatlining after years when councils
OL,17,Fand parents have been pitted against
OL,18,Feach other.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@ZOU
