OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,F"This government will take a different
OL,7,Fapproach, whether it's transforming
OL,8,Fthe early years to intervene earlier
OL,9,Fand deliver better outcomes for
OL,10,Fchildren, or launching our curriculum
OL,11,Fand assessment review to put high and
OL,12,Frising standards and inclusion
OL,13,Ftogether at the heart of every school.
OL,15,F"We will restore parents' trust that
OL,16,Ftheir child will get the support they
OL,17,Fneed in mainstream school, if that is
OL,18,Fthe right place for them. And that
OL,19,Fthere will always be a place in
OL,20,Fspecial schools for children with the
OL,21,Fmost complex needs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
