OL,3,C'It scares me what the future holds' -
OL,4,Cone mother's SEND school fight
OL,6,F"We have a broken system in desperate
OL,7,Fneed of long-term renewal. I won't
OL,8,Fmake false promises, change won't feel
OL,9,Fas quick as parents ` or I ` would
OL,10,Flike. I will make sure our approach is
OL,11,Ffully planned and delivered in concert
OL,12,Fwith parents, schools, councils, and
OL,13,Feveryone who works with children."
OL,15,FYou can hear the stories of other
OL,16,Ffamilies impacted by the SEND crisis
OL,17,Fand watch the full report on Sarah's
OL,18,Fexperience on ITVX.
